Cool about 10 minutes before serving. Makes about 6-8 servings.
This recipe may be divided in half if you need smaller portions.', 'https://www.foodista.com/recipe/2PC6VL3L/old-fashioned-mac-and-cheese-sundaysupper', 'Foodista.com – The Cooking Encyclopedia Everyone Can Edit', 'elbow macaroni
