Lightly whisk the eggs.
Mix and combine baking soda, spices, all-purpose, whole wheat and cake flour.
Add the lightly beaten eggs, flour and spices to the melted honey, sugar and butter mixture. Mix and combine to obtain smooth and soft dough.
