If you have leftovers in the freezer, thaw the ice cream at least 10 minutes before attempting to dig in because it will be much stiffer than store-bought ice cream.', 'https://www.foodista.com/recipe/SWTCJPT6/peach-coconut-ice-cream', 'Foodista.com – The Cooking Encyclopedia Everyone Can Edit', 'full-fat coconut milk
